high_descs: Turn right for two steps, turn right and walk straight to the white table and stop.
Pick up the salt shaker that is closest to the wall.
Turn left for one step, turn left for two steps, turn left to face the sink cabinet.
Open the bottom right cabinet under the sink, put the salt shaker in the cabinet in front of the pan in it, and shut the door.
Take three steps forward and stand in front of the sink cabinet.
Pick up the salt shaker by the spatula.
Turn around and walk three steps, turn around again and stop.
Open the bottom right cabinet door, place the salt shaker in about six inches from the existing salt shaker then shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers in the bottom right cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the white table on the other side of the room.
Pick up the rearmost salt shaker that is on the table.
Turn around, go forward, turn to the left to face the cabinet under the sink.
Put the salt in the cabinet under the sink.
Go forward to the counter that is left of the sink.
Pick up the salt that is on the counter.
Turn around, go forward, turn around to face the cabinet under the sink.
Put the salt in the cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and then turn to the right and go to the table.
Pick up the salt shaker off of the table.
Turn around and face the counter on the right.
Open the cabinet under the counter and place the salt shaker inside.
Step forward to the counter.
Pick up the other salt shaker off of the counter.
Turn around and Step back from the counter.
Open the cabinet under the counter and place the salt shaker inside.
anns.task_desc: Put away two salt shakers in a cabinet.
